params.name: feature_size
params.description: The feature dimension of the extracted features.

params.name: sampling_rate
params.description: The sampling rate at which the audio files should be digitalized expressed in hertz (Hz).

params.name: padding_value
params.description: The value that is used to fill the padding values.

params.name: do_normalize
params.description: Whether or not to zero-mean unit-variance normalize the input. Normalizing can help to significantlyimprove the performance for some models.

params.name: num_mel_bins
params.description: The number of mel-frequency bins in the extracted spectrogram features.

params.name: hop_length
params.description: Number of ms between windows. Otherwise referred to as shift in many papers.

params.name: win_function
params.description: Name for the window function used for windowing, must be accessible via torch.{win_function}

params.name: frame_signal_scale
params.description: Constant multiplied in creating the frames before applying DFT. This argument is deprecated.

params.name: mel_floor
params.description: Minimum value of mel frequency banks.

params.name: reduction_factor
params.description: Spectrogram length reduction factor. This argument is deprecated.

params.name: return_attention_mask
params.description: Whether or not call() should return attention_mask.
